reviews.review_text: Classic Venue Every show played at the Frost is worth a listen, even this one that begins with some major, uncorrected tempo issues for the first few songs. They pull it together for "Hey Pocky Way" and the "Let it Grow" jam gets hot. Still there are better shows to pick from at the Frost.
